## Really Cool Flash Game

A flash game viewer using Ruffle emulator. This page displays the Madness Combat Defense flash game with proper scaling and black borders for aspect ratio preservation.

### Game Details
- **Game**: Madness Combat Defense
- **Platform**: Ruffle (Flash emulator)
- **Source**: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/QiProject/flash-games@8a30ea684498b868a7b1cd188bd860ba2042eb56/Madness-Combat-Defense.swf

### Technical Info
- Uses Ruffle.js for Flash emulation
- Responsive sizing with 5.5:3 aspect ratio
- Black background with dynamic scaling
- Supports window resize events

### How It Works
The page loads a Ruffle player and streams the SWF file into a container with proper aspect ratio handling and black letterboxing.